<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1005645">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1005645/" class="title-link">徐向东写得很好</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1005645"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/avia/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1012334-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/avia/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">avia</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-09-27"
      class="main-meta">2005-09-27 09:40:54</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1005645_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  偶像的书，出版上市没几天就买了，这本书是徐向东的论文集，非常有趣而重要的一点是，徐向东将道德哲学视为政治哲学的根基，这令该书虽然在许多时候是一本政治哲学的引述性质的书的同时，也具有了它独特、重要的价值。同时，我希望看到徐向东更多展示其观点的哲学著作。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1005645/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1005645_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1005645_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
